      • multiplyDivide

        public static Expression multiplyDivide(Expression e,
                                        BigDecimal multiplier,
                                        BigDecimal divider)
        Multiplies an expression by a constant and divides by another constant, optimizing appropriately.

        For example, multiplyDivide(e, 10, 1000) returns e / 100.
